{
  "stem": "20142.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And many of our people who had any knowledge of building industry were engaged in it, and they were helping them out.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when the material was there, there was work going on 24 hours a day, two shifts, 12 hours a shift.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was working during the day, and the shift was from 6 o'clock in the morning till 6 o'clock at night.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then there was the night shift, what they call this, from 6 o'clock in the evening till 6 o'clock in the morning.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And a great amount of fatalities among our people were during the night shift, where people simply couldn't conduct themselves on a basis of delivering whatever was asked of them.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the kapo, if not the kapo, then the Germans took advantage of them, like hit them to a point of no, that they lost their consciences.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they were carried away to be liquidated.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The guards were awful.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were always walking around with a whip in their hand, or with an iron bar.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So if they didn't like any of your movement, they just hit you and hit you to the point that they could break either your bones or your back.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Or if they hit you in the head, they were definitely knocking the brain out of you.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was fortunate that I, I was somehow fast enough for them not to be hit or be molested.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, a SS man who did not like people who were-- who did not walk fast enough, especially when there was rainy days and they had the clogs, the Dutch shoes out of wood.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they couldn't move fast enough.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
